title: Search me
body:
Tomorrow's post is going to be a good one. Today's will not. Here's a list of Google searches where the Moxie Blog ranks on the first page, but probably shouldn't:

  • Slash pictures - I get at least 50 hits a day from this one

  • welcome back cotter

  • growing a beard

  • porn names

  • wehrenberg theme song

  • Scarlett Johansson's ass - this is the first in a theme of searches: add the word "ass" and you'll most likely be directed to this blog

  • you can't handle the truth

  • going to kansas city

  • Fructis commercial

  • ivory beaked woodpecker

  • peanut butter jelly and a baseball bat

  • parachute rope

  • ass-media - See!

  • make the pain go away

  • tiddles - I thought I made this word up

  • batten down the hatches

  • while you WEE sleeping - Wee... huh huh huh

  • lick this - short and sweet, just how I like my women

  • big wobbly boobies - Woo hoo!

  • hairiest man alive - this one brought me down a notch

  • what do hemroids look like - this one brought me down 17 notches

  • I'll be suck egg mule

  • going cinema with girl. what to do? - that's my personal favorite

  • carly patterson splits

  • Calvin Klein Escape market audience

  • going all in - winner for sexiest search EVER

  • rhinoceros poop - popular with my veterinarian readership

  • ass in slow motion clips - Another "ass" example

  • famous brothers Andersons, Paul and Wes - Moxie Blog: disseminating misinformation about famous directors since 2004

  • sciatic nerve ass - ass, ass, ass

  • beer bleeding - speaking of beer... I'm off to the fridge

  • Springfield cat burglar

  • sings Fur Elise

  • como te llama - wow, the second most common Spanish term in the world and this blog is the second link... I need to learn how to capitalize on that

  • twizzlers worth the walk - yes, they are

  • big fat guy at computer

  • firefox platterpus

  • maura tierney ass - the final "ass"... for now

  • Springfield's premiere porn theater

Strangely, the Moxie Blog didn't make Google's front page on any of these searches:

  • moxie

  • where's my hat?

  • Benzo

  • I'm AWESOME

  • Dan is the coolest man alive

I need to start Google bombing myself more often.
